dct_title_s: France and Belgium 1:50.000 / compiled and drawn by the Ordnance Survey.
dct_description_sm: Relief is shown by 5 meter contour interval and spot heights. The grid on this map is based on Nord de Guerre Zone. Map shows six classes of roads and paths, three classes of railroads, three types of internal boundaries, various types of vegetation, aerodromes and landing grounds, rivers, creeks, springs, canals, marshes, buildings, arms, towns with populations, and international and administrative boundaries. Sheets include index to adjoining sheets and Reliability diagram.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
